  <entry>
    <title>C++中的模板</title>
    <link href="/2026/06/11/C++/C++%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF/"/>
    <url>/2026/06/11/C++/C++%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>什么是C++模板？</p><p>模板（Template）是C++的一种泛型编程机制，允许你编写与类型无关的代码，编译器会根据实际使用的类型生成对应的代码。</p><p>用一句话理解：模板就是“代码的蓝图”，你写一个模板，编译器会根据你使用的类型生成具体的函数或类。</p><p>其中模板可以分为两类：函数模板和类模板。</p><h2 id="简单的函数模板"><a href="#简单的函数模板" class="headerlink" title="简单的函数模板"></a>简单的函数模板</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-comment">// 单类型模板函数</span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> T&gt;<br><span class="hljs-function">T <span class="hljs-title">add</span><span class="hljs-params">(T a, T b)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a + b;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-built_in">add</span>(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">5</span>) &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-built_in">add</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2.5</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3.1</span>) &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>1、<code>template &lt;typename T&gt;</code> 告诉编译器这是个模板，T是占位符。</p><p>2、add(T a, T b)：函数的参数和返回值都使用 T，在编译时会根据调用自动生成对应类型的函数。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-comment">// 多类型函数模板</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> T1, <span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> T2&gt;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">add</span><span class="hljs-params">(T1 a, T2 b)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    std::cout&lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&quot; a + b = &quot;</span>&lt;&lt;(a + b)&lt;&lt;std::endl;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">add</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">add</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1.3</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="类模板"><a href="#类模板" class="headerlink" title="类模板"></a>类模板</h2><p>用法和函数模板类似</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> T1, <span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> T2&gt;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">MyArray</span><br>&#123;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">MyArray</span>() = <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span>;<br>    ~<span class="hljs-built_in">MyArray</span>() = <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">setType1</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> index, T1 value)</span> </span>&#123; data[index] = value; &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">T1 <span class="hljs-title">getType1</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> index)</span> </span>&#123; <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> data[index]; &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">setType2</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> index, T2 value)</span> </span>&#123; buf[index] = value; &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">T2 <span class="hljs-title">getType2</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> index)</span> </span>&#123; <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> buf[index]; &#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">setType1</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> index, T1 value)</span> </span>&#123; data[index] = value; &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">T1 <span class="hljs-title">getType1</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> index)</span> </span>&#123; <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> data[index]; &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">setType2</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> index, T2 value)</span> </span>&#123; buf[index] = value; &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">T2 <span class="hljs-title">getType2</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> index)</span> </span>&#123; <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> buf[index]; &#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">private</span>:<br>    T1 data[<span class="hljs-number">10</span>];<br>    T2 buf[<span class="hljs-number">10</span>];<br>&#125;;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    MyArray&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>, <span class="hljs-type">double</span>&gt; arr;<br>    arr.<span class="hljs-built_in">setType1</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">42</span>);<br>    arr.<span class="hljs-built_in">setType2</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3.14</span>);<br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; arr.<span class="hljs-built_in">getType1</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>) &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; arr.<span class="hljs-built_in">getType2</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>) &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br><br>    MyArray&lt;<span class="hljs-type">float</span>, <span class="hljs-type">double</span>&gt; arr2;<br>    arr<span class="hljs-number">2.</span><span class="hljs-built_in">setType1</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">42.1F</span>);<br>    arr<span class="hljs-number">2.</span><span class="hljs-built_in">setType2</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3.14</span>);<br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; arr<span class="hljs-number">2.</span><span class="hljs-built_in">getType1</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>) &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; arr<span class="hljs-number">2.</span><span class="hljs-built_in">getType2</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>) &lt;&lt; std::endl;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="模板特化"><a href="#模板特化" class="headerlink" title="模板特化"></a>模板特化</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> T&gt;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">PrintValue</span><span class="hljs-params">(T a)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    std::cout&lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;a value is : &quot;</span>&lt;&lt;a&lt;&lt;std::endl;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">// 特化 int 类型</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;&gt;<br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">PrintValue</span>&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt;(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a)<br>&#123;<br>    std::cout&lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;a type is int ,value is : &quot;</span>&lt;&lt;a&lt;&lt;std::endl;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">PrintValue</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1.1F</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">PrintValue</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="非类型模板参数"><a href="#非类型模板参数" class="headerlink" title="非类型模板参数"></a>非类型模板参数</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span> N&gt;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">MyArray</span><br>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">MyArray</span>() = <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span>;<br>    ~<span class="hljs-built_in">MyArray</span>() = <span class="hljs-keyword">default</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">GetDataLen</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function">    </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;data len is : %zu\n&quot;</span>, N);<br>    &#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">private</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> data[N];<br>&#125;;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    MyArray&lt;<span class="hljs-number">10</span>&gt; tmp;<br>    tmp.<span class="hljs-built_in">GetDataLen</span>();<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="模板别名"><a href="#模板别名" class="headerlink" title="模板别名"></a>模板别名</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> T&gt;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> Vec = std::vector&lt;T&gt;;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    Vec&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; IntVec;<br>    IntVec.<span class="hljs-built_in">push_back</span>(<span class="hljs-number">10</span>);<br>    Vec&lt;<span class="hljs-type">float</span>&gt; FloatVec;<br>    FloatVec.<span class="hljs-built_in">push_back</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0.1F</span>);<br><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;int type vec val is : %d\n&quot;</span>, IntVec.<span class="hljs-built_in">front</span>());<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;float type vec val is : %f\n&quot;</span>, FloatVec.<span class="hljs-built_in">front</span>());<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="模板元编程"><a href="#模板元编程" class="headerlink" title="模板元编程"></a>模板元编程</h2><p>模板元编程是利用模板在编译期执行计算的技术。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span> N&gt;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">struct</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Factorial</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">constexpr</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> val = N * Factorial&lt;N <span class="hljs-number">-1</span>&gt;::val;<br>&#125;;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">//模板特化</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;&gt;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">struct</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Factorial</span>&lt;<span class="hljs-number">0</span>&gt;<br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">constexpr</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> val = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>&#125;;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Factorial is : %d\n&quot;</span>, Factorial&lt;<span class="hljs-number">5</span>&gt;::val);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="SFINAE-与-enable-if"><a href="#SFINAE-与-enable-if" class="headerlink" title="SFINAE 与 enable_if"></a>SFINAE 与 enable_if</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;type_traits&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> T&gt;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">auto</span> <span class="hljs-title">foo</span><span class="hljs-params">(T n)</span> -&gt; <span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> std::enable_if&lt;std::is_integral&lt;T&gt;::value, T&gt;::type</span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> n * <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    std::cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-built_in">foo</span>(<span class="hljs-number">5</span>) &lt;&lt; std::endl;    <span class="hljs-comment">// OK, int是整型</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// std::cout &lt;&lt; foo(3.14);           // 编译失败，double不是整型</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">/*</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">std::is_integral&lt;T&gt; 判断类型T是否是整数类型，判断结果(true/false)放在 std::is_integral&lt;T&gt;::value中</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"></span><br><span class="hljs-comment">std::enable_if&lt;true, T&gt;::type  // 等于 T</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">std::enable_if&lt;false, T&gt;::type // 不存在 编译时候就报错</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"></span><br><span class="hljs-comment">*/</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="变长参数模板"><a href="#变长参数模板" class="headerlink" title="变长参数模板"></a>变长参数模板</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">print</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;----is over\n&quot;</span>);<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span>&lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> T, <span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span>... Args&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">print</span><span class="hljs-params">(T frist, Args... args)</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    std::cout&lt;&lt; frist;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(<span class="hljs-keyword">sizeof</span>...(args) &gt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>)<br>    &#123;<br>        std::cout&lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;, &quot;</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(args...);<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,<span class="hljs-number">4</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1.5</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;hello&quot;</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
